1
00:00:12,700 --> 00:00:15,400
OK. I'll tell him you called.
好的. 我会告诉他你来过电话.

2
00:00:20,900 --> 00:00:22,900
Hey, that was Lisa.
Hey, 刚才是Lisa.

3
00:00:23,100 --> 00:00:24,600
She said you were supposed to meet her.
她说你本来要跟她见面的.

4
00:00:24,700 --> 00:00:26,938
I know. I was. Was she mad?
我知道. 我是要跟她见面. 她生气了吗?

5
00:00:27,086 --> 00:00:29,254
Was she mad!
她生气了吗!

6
00:00:29,403 --> 00:00:32,275
Oh boy, I blew it.
Oh boy, 我把一切搞砸了.

7
00:00:32,452 --> 00:00:35,078
Well, she said she was going home and she'd call you later.
Well, 她说她要回家, 会再给你打电话.

8
00:00:35,229 --> 00:00:37,180
What happened?
发生了什么事?

9
00:00:37,376 --> 00:00:39,678
I taped in the Square this morning.
我今天上午在广场拍片.

10
00:00:39,813 --> 00:00:43,113
Then I had a meeting over at school with my advisor.
然后去学校见了我的导师.

11
00:00:43,251 --> 00:00:45,943
First of all, he was 45 minutes late.
首先, 他迟到了45分钟.

12
00:00:46,097 --> 00:00:52,083
Then after a complete progress report, he decides to go over the whole project from the top.
接着, 在我做了完整的进度报告之后, 他决定要从头开始审查整个项目.

13
00:00:52,255 --> 00:00:53,764
What a pain!
真是讨厌!

14
00:00:53,889 --> 00:00:57,475
I wanted to just get up and walk out.
我当时就想起身走人.

15
00:00:57,623 --> 00:01:01,663
Temper, Michael. He is your graduate advisor.
冷静, Michael. 他可是你的研究生导师.

16
00:01:01,826 --> 00:01:04,618
Lisa will calm down.
Lisa会冷静下来的. 

17
00:01:04,773 --> 00:01:08,210
It's nothing a little gesture on your part won't fix.
你只需稍微表示表示就能补救这一切.

18
00:01:09,760 --> 00:01:11,470
Ask her to marry you.
向她求婚吧.

19
00:01:11,610 --> 00:01:14,197
Let's not go to extremes.
别走极端.

20
00:01:14,320 --> 00:01:16,520
Tell her it'll never happen again.
向她保证再也不会发生这种事.

21
00:01:16,690 --> 00:01:18,475
I told her that the last time.
我上次就跟她这么说过了.

22
00:01:18,656 --> 00:01:21,862
Well well well, you do have a problem, don't you?
Well well well, 你确实碰到了难题, 是吧?

23
00:01:21,990 --> 00:01:24,073
I could grovel.
我可以低声下气求她原谅.

24
00:01:24,200 --> 00:01:28,433
Groveling is an option. Now, personally I don't grovel.
这也是一个办法. 就我个人而言, 我从不低声下气求人.

25
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:31,382
I just inspire women to break up with me.
我只会促使女人与我分手.

26
00:01:33,700 --> 00:01:35,600
Maybe you should try groveling.
也许你应该试试低声下气.

